channel.description:
I was wondering what I would get for this account if I were to sell it for either more RSGP or IRL cash:
[img]http://screensnapr.com/e/xtyrjW.png[/img]
I don't feel like showing picture of the bank because it's packed, but for the most part, it has elite void, chaotic maul and rapier, dragon defender etc., otherwise there isn't a lot of special items on it.
So I was wondering what I could get out of it?
